  "2360090": {
    "name": "Boardquest: Tales of Liria",
    "steam_appid": 2360090,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lead Orcs, Humans, Elves, Demons, Undead or Dwarves in their quest to rule over Liria in this epic high-fantasy strategy RPG for 1-4 players.</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now available:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💎 <strong>TUTORIAL</strong> 💎 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💎 <strong>PVE</strong> 💎 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💎 <strong>LOCAL MULTIPLAYER</strong> 💎</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💎 <strong>Online MULTIPLAYER</strong> 💎  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💎 <strong>CAMPAIGN</strong> 💎 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Command Your Beloved Factions</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose between <strong>Orcs</strong>, <strong>Humans</strong>, <strong>Elves</strong>, and <strong>Demons</strong> and use their unique abilities and play styles to <strong>seize control over Liria</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>HUMANS</strong>: as <strong>Gregor the Mighty</strong>, the legendary fighter, you will inspire your army towards attack and throw yourself right in the middle of action.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>ORCS</strong>: As <strong>Bilar Crosschain</strong>, the Orc Shaman, you will tap into ancestral magic to sustain your army through battle.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>ELVES</strong>: As <strong>Daria Nightshade</strong>, the arcane Elven sorceress, you will use your powers to protect your people and keep the woods of Numiria safe.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>DEMONS</strong>: As <strong>Raegar</strong>, the Demon lord, you will manipulate the life and death points of your enemies and foes. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DWARVES</strong>: As <strong>Gnut Hammerfist</strong>, the Dwarven Fighter and Engineer, you will brew potions and give courage to your friends while engaging in melee combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>UNDEAD</strong>: As <strong>Queen Freya</strong>, the Undead Queen, you will exhaust your friends and draw the life out of your foes.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360090/extras/1522812c06f5e46e2b87446ac2245b9d.poster.avif?t=1769770464\" width=482 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360090/extras/1522812c06f5e46e2b87446ac2245b9d.webm?t=1769770464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360090/extras/1522812c06f5e46e2b87446ac2245b9d.mp4?t=1769770464\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Master Powerful Weapons</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fire Axe, Amulet of Fate, Shadow Shield and many others await you: collect treasure chests and fight monsters to uncover <strong>legendary weapons and artefacts</strong> your units can equip.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360090/extras/81aff036ce90927c8ca30a471c4a51c9.poster.avif?t=1769770464\" width=482 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360090/extras/81aff036ce90927c8ca30a471c4a51c9.webm?t=1769770464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360090/extras/81aff036ce90927c8ca30a471c4a51c9.mp4?t=1769770464\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Channel Ancestral Magic</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take advantage of your commander's <strong>unique powers</strong> to inspire your units, protect them from harm, or cause destruction on your enemies. Advance your level and <strong>unlock additional abilities</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360090/extras/2f25d8f79226cd09f2f6a01aa46dcc33.poster.avif?t=1769770464\" width=482 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360090/extras/2f25d8f79226cd09f2f6a01aa46dcc33.webm?t=1769770464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360090/extras/2f25d8f79226cd09f2f6a01aa46dcc33.mp4?t=1769770464\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Defeat Nasty Monsters</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The beautiful land of Liria is infested by monstrous creatures: some more common than others – like Goblins and Lizards – and some rare, like Balthazar, an ancient fearsome dragon. Defeat them and collect <strong>gold, loot, and XP points</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360090/extras/2064216c4bc451ac4531cc08b7983481.poster.avif?t=1769770464\" width=482 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360090/extras/2064216c4bc451ac4531cc08b7983481.webm?t=1769770464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360090/extras/2064216c4bc451ac4531cc08b7983481.mp4?t=1769770464\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unleash Epic Battles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Liria is a shape-shifting land: every session plays on a <strong>different map</strong>, making every scenario unique and challenging.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360090/extras/6c536037819f56bf93cf3c23ce2560c9.poster.avif?t=1769770464\" width=482 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360090/extras/6c536037819f56bf93cf3c23ce2560c9.webm?t=1769770464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2360090/extras/6c536037819f56bf93cf3c23ce2560c9.mp4?t=1769770464\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
